    "For example, the following puzzle tests understanding programming semantics to predict a system's behaviour: def mystery (x): return x // 2 print (mystery (10))",
    "Commonsense Reasoning Puzzles depict typical situations omitting key details.",
    "Solvers must explain events by inferring plausible implicit assumptions about motivations, causes and effects.",
    "For instance, the question \"A man who was outside in the rain without an umbrella or hat didn't get a single hair on his head wet.",
    "requires pragmatic analysis of unstated contextual factors."
